                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000092c614b2-c466-44bb-b400-d8f8efad4bfb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000192c614b2-c466-44bb-b400-d8f8efad4bfb"><img src="data:image/png;base64," style="width: 0.9444444in;height: 0.6476192in;" alt="Picture 1" /></span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000292c614b2-c466-44bb-b400-d8f8efad4bfb"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000092c614b2-c466-44bb-b400-d8f8efad4bfb {line-height: 150.0%;margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-00000192c614b2-c466-44bb-b400-d8f8efad4bfb {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000292c614b2-c466-44bb-b400-d8f8efad4bfb {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000429ab52-cbc4-43e8-8ff4-07dd872e748f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({13}^{2}={5}^{2}+{12}^{2};\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000010429ab52-cbc4-43e8-8ff4-07dd872e748f"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(θ=90^{\circ} \) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000429ab52-cbc4-43e8-8ff4-07dd872e748f {line-height: 150.0%;margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000010429ab52-cbc4-43e8-8ff4-07dd872e748f {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ec72956a-4981-47b3-82da-304dfb31300b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ec72956a-4981-47b3-82da-304dfb31300b">ZvB,  </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\overrightarrow{A}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ec72956a-4981-47b3-82da-304dfb31300b"> I </span><span class="math-tex" styl