                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000007142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(A\left(x,y\right),\ B\left({x}^{{'}},{y}^{{'}}\right)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0"> Ges </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(C\left(x-{x}^{{'}},y-{y}^{{'}}\right)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0"> </span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">we</span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">›</span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">`y</span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">&#184;</span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">‡</span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">jv mg</span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">‡</span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">iL n</span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">‡</span><span class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">j</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0">: </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({m}_{AB}={m}_{BC}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0"> n‡e|</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000027142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0 {line-height: 150.0%;margin-bottom: 0;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000017142bd7f-43de-4680-bce5-fd2cc360d1d0 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: