                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000001956f9c6-5f15-4ab1-a82d-92b4dae270e0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000011956f9c6-5f15-4ab1-a82d-92b4dae270e0">Ans:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000021956f9c6-5f15-4ab1-a82d-92b4dae270e0"> Machinery</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001956f9c6-5f15-4ab1-a82d-92b4dae270e0 {line-height: 150.0%;margin-bottom: 0;text-align: left;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000011956f9c6-5f15-4ab1-a82d-92b4dae270e0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000021956f9c6-5f15-4ab1-a82d-92b4dae270e0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
